erface:**\n- `Complete(ctx, systemPrompt, userPrompt) (string, error)`\n\n**CommandLLMClient:**\n- `Command`: string (path to LLM executable)\n- `Args`: []string (additional args)\n- Invokes LLM with:\n  - `-p` flag (print/non-interactive mode)\n  - `--system-prompt <system>` (if non-empty)\n  - `--output-format text`\n  - User prompt via stdin\n\n### 10. EVOLUTION PACKAGE FILES\n\nAll in `/workspace/internal/evolution/`:\n- `types.go` (57 lines): Type definitions\n- `trigger.go` (64 lines): Debounce trigger\n- `trigger_test.go`: Tests for trigger\n- `collector.go` (92 lines): Data collection\n- `classifier.go` (51 lines): Run classification\n- `reflector.go` (130 lines): Lesson extraction\n- `curator.go` (195 lines): Prompt curation\n- `audit.go` (174 lines): Logging and snapshots\n- `scriptgen.go` (114 lines): Script generation\n- `llmclient.go` (59 lines): LLM command wrapper\n- `orchestrator.go` (249 lines): Pipeline coordination\n- `evolution_test.go` (1199 lines): Comprehensive unit tests\n- `corruption_test.go` (33732 bytes): Corruption/resilience tests\n- `scriptgen_test.go`: Script generation tests\n- Total: ~3550 lines of Go code\n\n### 11. TESTING\n\n**Unit Tests:** `/workspace/internal/evolution/evolution_test.go`\n- Tests for each pipeline stage (Collector, Classifier, Reflector, Curator, ScriptGenerator)\n- Tests for AuditLogger (JSONL logging, snapshots, knowledge base)\n- Tests for code fence stripping, conversational response detection\n- Tests for lesson deduplication and already-applied lesson filtering\n- End-to-end orchestrator tests including new step addition\n- Tests for duplicate step prevention and workflow graph validation\n\n**Integration Tests:** `/workspace/test/integration/evolution_test.go`\n- Full pipeline integration test\n- Project setup and execution verification\n\n### 12. KEY INTEGRATION FLOW\n\n1. **Run Completion** → `trackRun()` in grpc/server.go\n2. **Fire Evolution Trigger** → `s.evolution.Fire(projectDir, workflowName, run