{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QmDNQuYzePC7jyPowTGLzE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**New file:** `internal/evolution/population.go`\n- `PopulationConfig` — enables population mode with configurable size and promotion threshold\n- `Candidate` — prompt variant with fitness, runs count, generation tracking\n- `Assignment` — records which candidate was used for which run\n- `Population` — manages candidates, selection, scoring, promotion, and snapshot/restore\n- `SelectCandidate()` — fitness-proportionate selection with exploration bonus for under-tested candidates\n- `ScoreAndPromote()` — updates running-average fitness and promotes candidates exceeding threshold\n- `ApplyCandidate()` / `RestoreSnapshot()` — swaps prompt content with snapshot for rollback\n- `FirstPromptPath()` — extracts the first `file()` reference from a workflow\n\n**Modified:** `internal/config/config.go`\n- Added `PopulationConfig` struct with `enabled`, `size`, `promotion_threshold` fields\n- Nested it in `EvolutionConfig` as `Population`\n\n**Modified:** `cmd/cloched/main.go`\n- Added `initPopulation()` that reads `PopulationConfig` from project config and creates a `Population` instance\n- Wired it into the server via `srv.SetPopulation(pop)`\n\n**Modified:** `internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`\n- Added `population` field and `SetPopulation()` setter\n- **Pre-run hook** in `launchAndTrack()`: before `container.Start()`, selects a candidate and applies it to the base prompt path (with snapshot)\n- **Post-run hook** in `trackRun()`: after `evolution.Fire()`, calls `ScoreAndPromote()` and restores snapshot if not promoted\n\n**New file:** `internal/evolution/population_test.go`\n- Unit tests for load/save, selection, apply, restore, scoring, promotion\n- End-to-end test simulating 4 runs through the full select → apply → score → promote/restore cycle\n\n**Version bump:** `1.14.1` → `1.15.0`\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":392,"cache_read_input_tokens":66634,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":392},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"20d5adfa-ca6e-4c90-b84e-e05e5aa65257","uuid":"85209d21-7807-440d-8137-8c13ba5d3047"}
